<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>老麦笔记 - Mastodon 系列</title><description>这里是老麦的个人博客，分享生活、热爱生活、享受生活，主打真实与平淡。 // Mastodon 系列订阅</description><link>https://www.iamlm.com/</link><item><title>老麦于2026/05/30的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116662712793547434/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116662712793547434/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;“你只是慢热内敛、不爱主动奔赴，不是不懂人情，更不是不会做人。&lt;br /&gt;顺其自然相处，愿意来的人自然留在身边，就很好。”&lt;br /&gt;听到最暖心的评价。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 09:02:05 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/05/22的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116619101592117226/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116619101592117226/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;是的，被束缚的永远只是自己而已。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 May 2026 16:11:11 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/05/17的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116591433613415931/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116591433613415931/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;既然睡不着，那就「开整」。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.laomai.org/media_attachments/files/116/591/426/114/017/629/original/218196d931886290.png&quot; alt=&quot;小龙虾&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 18:54:52 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/05/09的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116546170706572715/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116546170706572715/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;祝所有的母亲节日快乐。辛苦了～&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 19:03:54 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/05/05的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116523264209149197/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116523264209149197/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;假期的尾巴追完《剑来》第二季，感叹一下现在的国漫是拍得真好。⭐️ ⭐️ ⭐️ ⭐️ ⭐️&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 17:58:29 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/05/04的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116518521349327426/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116518521349327426/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;恭喜吴宜泽。太刺激了，半决赛，决赛都打满且顺利拿下，大心脏，毫不手软的进攻，真的精彩。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:52:19 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/04/30的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116495631712945764/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116495631712945764/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;小吴今晚生吃艾伦，简直头皮发麻。好样的，就是要强势点。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 20:51:11 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/04/21的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116443658994321925/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116443658994321925/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;开了几个月摩托车，再次开回电鸡，感觉自己在骑狗。没办法，摩托车被老婆征用了，以后想骑摩托车只能等礼拜了。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:33:50 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/04/14的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116405492094922493/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116405492094922493/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我去，真把自己看得太高了，又被现实狠狠的上了一课。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 22:47:29 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/04/12的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116392765450664698/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116392765450664698/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;最近老是叫老婆陪我喝两杯小酒，导致她皮肤又开始过敏。错了，太过放肆要承担后果呢。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 16:50:56 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>